content: महिषी {@--1@} A she-buffalo, buffalocow; <ls>Ms. 9. 55</ls>; <ls>Y. 2. 159.</ls> {@--2@} The principal queen, queen-consort; महिषीसखः <ls>R. 1. 48</ls>, <ls n="R.">2. 25</ls>, <ls n="R.">3. 9.</ls> {@--3@} A queen in general. {@--4@} The female of a bird. {@--5@} A lady's maid, female servant (सैरिंध्री). {@--6@} An immoral woman. {@--7@} Money acquired by the prostitution of one's wife; <ab>cf.</ab> माहिषिक.
